festival choir which will sing at a Mass for those with
Special Needs, Saturday, March 23, at 11:00am;
Archbishop Sartain, presider. Rehearsal will be Monday,
March 18, 6:00-7:30pm. <i>Information</i>, 
<a href="mailto:musicoffice@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Festival Chorus for the Mass for Those with Special Needs">
Music Office</a>, 206-382-4874.</p>
