spring Blood Drive, Tuesday, April 16, 2013. This
spring’s blood drive is in memory of Frank Robl, a
founding member of the Cathedral’s Health and
Healing Ministry, who died in January after a long
battle with cancer. Sign ups will be at coffee hours on
April 7 and April 14. <i>Information</i>, 
<a href="mailto:jsimpson@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Spring Blood Drive">John Simpson</a>, 206-274-3173.</p>
