meditation. Open to all, come as you are, as often as
you can. We will meet on six Tuesday mornings from
April 9 through May 14, 10:30-Noon, 2nd floor
Cathedral Place. <i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:tbowen@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=The Fire of Christ's Love">
